    "body" : "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/google/guava\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Guava</a> makes this easy with <a href=\"http://google.github.io/guava/releases/snapshot/api/docs/com/google/common/base/Throwables.html#getStackTraceAsString-java.lang.Throwable-\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Throwables.getStackTraceAsString(Throwable)</a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Exception e = ...\nString stackTrace = Throwables.getStackTraceAsString(e);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Internally, this does what @Zach L suggests.</p>\n"
