    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use the <code>ExceptionUtils.getStackTrace(Throwable t);</code> from Apache Commons 3 class <code>org.apache.commons.lang3.exception.ExceptionUtils</code>. </p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/javadocs/api-3.1/org/apache/commons/lang3/exception/ExceptionUtils.html#getStackTrace(java.lang.Throwable)\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ExceptionUtils.getStackTrace(Throwable t)</a></p>\n\n<p>Code example: </p>\n\n<pre><code>try {\n\n  // your code here\n\n} catch(Exception e) {\n  String s = ExceptionUtils.getStackTrace(e);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
