    "body" : "<p>Use the apache commons-lang3 lib</p>\n\n<pre><code>import org.apache.commons.lang3.exception.ExceptionUtils;\n\n//...\n\nString[] ss = ExceptionUtils.getRootCauseStackTrace(e);\nlogger.error(StringUtils.join(ss, System.lineSeparator()));\n</code></pre>\n"
